{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1978,"month":5,"day":14}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"扶摇万里的大鹏——写在“航空兵英雄中队”","authors":["毕长龙"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里长空，摆下威武阵容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两军对垒，震动蓝天云层。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长空中展开一场比武，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观战的人望酸了脖颈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“千里眼”，占位有利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“神炮手”，左右开弓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“铁杆僚机”，扯起一道闪电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“空中猎手”，追捕一只秃鹰……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着这高空中的“厮杀”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们的心潮怎能平静？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是这些技术能手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却被林彪、“四人帮”横加罪名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练，长空里把战刀磨利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练，风雨中把翅膀练硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虽然没有“尖子”的名称，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要练出“尖子”的本领！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于，春风摇绿了杨柳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雷将大地唤醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席抓纲治军的英明决策，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我们的“尖子”恢复了名声！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，我们革命的尖兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶摇万里的大鹏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要党一声令下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们就是密布蓝天的刀丛！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}